 Del\u010dev|Stadion Goce Delchev]], [[Prilep]]\n|align=center|3,000\n|-\n|align=center|[[2011\u201312 Macedonian Football Cup|2011\u201312]]\n!scope=row|[[KF Renova|Renova]] (1)\n|align=center|3\u20131\n|[[FK Rabotni\u010dki|Rabotnichki]]\n|[[Gradski stadion \u0160tip|Gradski stadion]], [[Shtip]]\n|align=center|1,000\n|-\n|align=center|[[2012\u201313 Macedonian Football Cup|2012\u201313]]\n!scope=row|[[FK Teteks|Teteks]] (2)\n|align=center style=\"background-color:#cedff2\"|1\u20131 ([[Overtime (sports)|a.e.t.]]), <br> 6\u20135 [[Penalty shoot-out (association football)|pen.]]\n|[[KF Shk\u00ebndija|Shk\u00ebndija]]\n|[[To\u0161e Proeski Arena|Philip II Arena]], [[Skopje]]\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[2013\u201314 Macedonian Football Cup|2013\u201314]]\n!scope=row style=\"background-color:#fff4a7\"| [[FK Rabotni\u010dki|Rabotnichki]] {{double dagger}} (3)\n|align=center|2\u20130\n|[[FK Metalurg Skopje|Metalurg]]\n|[[To\u0161e Proeski Arena|Philip II Arena]], [[Skopje]]\n|align=center|1,000\n|-\n|align=center|[[2014\u201315 Macedonian Football Cup|2014\u201315]]\n!scope=row|[[FK Rabotni\u010dki|Rabotnichki]] (4)\n|align=center|2\u20131\n|[[FK Teteks|Teteks]]\n|[[To\u0161e Proeski Arena|Philip II Arena]], [[Skopje]]\n|align=center|3,800\n|-\n|align=center|[[2015\u201316 Macedonian Football Cup|2015\u201316]]\n!scope=row|[[KF Shk\u00ebndija|Shk\u00ebndija]] (1)\n|align=center|2\u20130\n|[[FK Rabotni\u010dki|Rabotnichki]]\n|[[To\u0161e Proeski Arena|Philip II Arena]], [[Skopje]]\n|align=center|8,000\n|-\n|align=center|[[2016\u201317 Macedonian Football Cup|2016\u201317]]\n!scope=row|[[FK Pelister|Pelister]] (2)\n|align=center style=\"background-color:#cedff2\"|0\u20130 ([[Overtime (sports)|a.e.t.]]), <br> 4\u20133 [[Penalty shoot-out (association football)|pen.]]\n|[[KF Shk\u00ebndija|Shk\u00ebndija]]\n|[[Stadion Mladost, Strumica|Stadion Mladost]], [[Strumica]]\n|align=center|6,000\n|-\n|align=center|[[2017\u201318 Macedonian Football Cup|2017\u201318]]\n!scope=row style=\"background-color:#fff4a7\"| [[KF Shk\u00ebndija|Shk\u00ebndija]] {{double dagger}} (2)\n|align=center|3\u20130\n|[[FK Pelister|Pelister]]\n|[[Stadion Mladost, Strumica|Stadion Mladost]], [[Strumica]]\n|align=center|2,500\n|-\n|align=center|[[2018\u201319 Macedonian Football Cup|2018\u201319]]\n!scope=row|[[Akademija Pandev]] (1)\n|align=center style=\"background-color:#cedff2\"|2\u20132 ([[Overtime (sports)|a.e.t.]]), <br> 4\u20132 [[Penalty shoot-out (association football)|pen.]]\n|[[FK Makedonija Gjor\u010de Petrov|Makedonija GP]]\n|[[To\u0161e Proeski Arena|Toshe Proeski Arena]], [[Skopje]]\n|align=center|3,000\n|}\n\nSources:<ref name=\"Winners\">{{cite web|title=Macedonia - List of Cup Finals|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesf/fyromcuphist.html|publisher=RSSSF|accessdate=12 July 2011}}</ref><ref name=\"Winners2\">{{cite web|title=Macedonian Football &#124; Macedonian Cup history&nbsp;\u2013 Macedonian Football|url=http://macedonianfootball.com/macedonian-cup-history/|publisher=MacedonianFootball.com|accessdate=30 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Performance by club==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Club\n! Winners\n! Runners-up\n! Winning Years\n! Runner-up Years\n|-\n| [[FK Vardar|Vardar]]\n| 5\n| 1\n| 1993, 1995, 1998, 1999, 2007\n| 1996\n|-bgcolor=#EEEEEE\n| [[FK Rabotni\u010dki|Rabotnichki]]\n| 4\n| 3\n| 2008, 2009, 2014, 2015\n| 2010, 2012, 2016\n|-\n| [[FK Sloga Jugomagnat|Sloga Jugomagnat]]{{ref label|Sloga|A|}}\n| 3\n| 5\n| 1996, 2000, 2004\n| 1997, 1998, 1999, 2001, 2003\n|-bgcolor=#EEEEEE\n| [[FK Pelister|Pelister]]\n| 2\n| 3\n| 2001, 2017\n| 1993, 1994, 2018\n|-\n| [[KF Shk\u00ebndija|Shk\u00ebndija]]\n| 2\n| 3\n| 2016, 2018\n| 2006, 2013, 2017\n|-bgcolor=#EEEEEE\n| [[FK Teteks|Teteks]]\n| 2\n| 2\n| 2010, 2013\n| 2011, 2015\n|-\n| [[FK Sileks|Sileks]]\n| 2\n| 1\n| 1994, 1997\n| 1995\n|-bgcolor=#EEEEEE\n| [[FK Pobeda|Pobeda]]{{ref label|Pobeda|B|}}\n| 1\n| 2\n| 2002\n| 2000, 2007\n|-\n| [[FK Makedonija Gjor\u010de Petrov|Makedonija Gjorche Petrov]]